high_descs: Turn to the right and find the sink.
Pick up the fork to the left of the sink.
Place the fork in the green glass on the left side of the sink.
Pick up the glass and fork from the sink.
Take the glass and back up a few steps.
Place the glass to the back of the counter, to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a glass and fork from the sink to the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the fork from the counter top by the sink.
Put the fork in the green cup which is in the left sink basin.
Pick the green cup out of the sink basin.
Walk to the counter top to the right of the sink.
Place the cup on the counter top, to the right of the large knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a fork in it on a counter top in a kitchen.

high_descs: turn right and go to face the kitchen sink
pick up the fork to the left of the sink
place the fork in the green bowl located in the sink
pick up the green bowl in the sink
move to the right side of the sink
place the green bowl to the right of the knife
anns.task_desc: place a fork in a bowl and move it to the other side of the sink
